title: 关于ESS的报错
author: 梦雨灵
txt_content:
[21:13:56 WARN]: [Essentials] "Essentials v2.0.1-b460" has registered a listener for org.bukkit.event.player.PlayerPickupItemEvent on method "public void com.earth2me.essentials.EssentialsPlayerListener.onPlayerPickupItem(org.bukkit.event.player.PlayerPickupItemEvent)", but the event is Deprecated. "Server performance will be affected"; please notify the authors [Zenexer, ementalo, Aelux, Brettflan, KimKandor, snowleo, ceulemans, Xeology, KHobbits, md_5, Iaccidentally, drtshock, vemacs, SupaHam].
[21:13:56 INFO]: [Essentials] Starting Metrics. Opt-out using the global PluginMetrics config.
[21:13:56 INFO]: [Vault][Economy] Essentials Economy hooked.
[21:13:56 INFO]: [Essentials] Using Vault based permissions (GroupManager)
[21:13:57 INFO]: [EssentialsProtect] Enabling EssentialsProtect v2.0.1-b460
[21:13:57 INFO]: [EssentialsChat] Enabling EssentialsChat v2.0.1-b460
[21:13:57 INFO]: [EssentialsAntiBuild] Enabling EssentialsAntiBuild v2.0.1-b460
[21:13:57 WARN]: [EssentialsAntiBuild] "EssentialsAntiBuild v2.0.1-b460" has registered a listener for org.bukkit.event.player.PlayerPickupItemEvent on method "public void com.earth2me.essentials.antibuild.EssentialsAntiBuildListener.onPlayerPickupItem(org.bukkit.event.player.PlayerPickupItemEvent)", but the event is Deprecated. "Server performance will be affected"; please notify the authors [Zenexer, ementalo, Aelux, Brettflan, KimKandor, snowleo, ceulemans, Xeology, KHobbits, Iaccidentally].

虽然这报错对服务器没啥影响，但还是想解决一下
